### Tracker + last 5 runs
GET http://localhost:4102/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=name eq 'ExchangeRates'&$expand=runs($orderby=startTime desc;$top=5)

### Status convenience function
GET http://localhost:4102/pipeline/status(name='ExchangeRates')

### Flush — reset the tracker and clear the local table.
POST http://localhost:4102/pipeline/flush
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ExchangeRates"}
